'''John "Jack" Hirst''' is a former professional [[rugby league]] [[footballer]] of the 1920s who at representative level has played for [[England national rugby league team|England]], and at club level for [[Featherstone Rovers]].

==International Honours==
Jack Hirst won a cap for [[England national rugby league team|England]] while at Featherstone Rovers in 1923 against Wales.<ref name="International Statistics at englandrl.co.uk">{{cite web|url=http://www.englandrl.co.uk/international_stats.php?GBSearch=Hirst&EnSearch=Hirst&submit_x=7&submit_y=3&submit.x=7&submit.y=8|title=International Statistics at englandrl.co.uk|publisher=englandrl|date=2008-12-31|accessdate=2009-01-01}}</ref>

